          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/repudiation",
          "message": { "text": "The Process could repudiate Companion Response emissions if the architecture lacks integrity-protected emission logging — a high-impact concern in wellness-conversation contexts where disputed emissions could include advisory content, distress responses, or persona-boundary assertions.", "markdown": "Implement integrity-protected emission logging with cryptographic chaining. Configure deterministic content hashing for every Companion Response." },
