          "message": { "text": "The Process could disclose sensitive information through Companion Response emissions — including system prompts, persona configuration details, prior user disclosures from session memory, or backend infrastructure metadata leaked through error responses. Cross-user information disclosure is a high-impact threat in wellness-conversation contexts.", "markdown": "Implement output sanitization layer scrubbing sensitive metadata from emissions. Configure strict session isolation preventing cross-user persona state leakage." },
