          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/information-disclosure",
          "message": { "text": "An attacker with audit log read access could disclose interaction event records exposing user interaction patterns, distress-signal frequency, escalation events, and dependency-risk indicators tied to identifiable users.", "markdown": "Implement at-rest encryption on the audit log with separate key management. Configure least-privilege access controls. Implement record-level field redaction for sensitive interaction fields." },
