          "message": { "text": "An attacker could deny service to the session store through high-volume write operations, storage exhaustion, or query patterns triggering database lock contention — preventing persona state persistence and restoration.", "markdown": "Implement per-user write rate limiting on session store operations. Configure storage quotas per user. Deploy database replication with automatic failover." },
