          "ruleId": "tachi/ai/agentic-threats",
          "message": { "text": "Hypothetical: the wellness-conversation companion emits wellness-coaching content to End Users without per-claim confidence-attestation or source-grounding indication. Indicators B and D structurally present; no confidence-threshold gate; no source-attestation requirement; no refusal pattern for low-confidence wellness claims. Authority-attestation sub-class per FR-004(e). Per OWASP ASI09:2026 and CWE-345, authority-claim emission without attestation may drive a user to act on an unverified wellness recommendation.", "markdown": "Implement a confidence-threshold gate on wellness-coaching emission with confidence display. Configure source-attestation requirement. Enable a refusal pattern for wellness claims below confidence threshold. Implement a calibrated-confidence layer with Expected Calibration Error monitor." },
