        {
          "ruleId": "tachi/ai/agentic-threats",
          "message": { "text": "Hypothetical: the wellness-conversation companion maintains a persistent named persona across multi-turn dialogues with End Users via the Conversation Session Store. Indicator C structurally present. No persona-memory timeout; no identity-impersonation refusal pattern; no persona-anchor at conversation start; no persona-prompt validation rejecting non-AI-identity assertions. Persona-boundary sub-class per FR-004(e). Per CWE-287 and CWE-290, the absence of persona-boundary validation enables impersonation that bypasses authentication-by-consistency.", "markdown": "Implement a persona-memory timeout. Configure an identity-impersonation refusal pattern. Enable a persona-anchor declaration enforced at every conversation start. Implement a persona-prompt validation step that rejects persona configurations asserting non-AI identity or unverified professional credentials." },
